            <p>Ab, antibodies; CPR, C&#x2010;peptide; DKA, diabetic ketoacidosis; F, female; GAD, glutamic acid decarboxylase; HbA1c, hemoglobin A1c; HLA, human leukocyte antigen; IA&#x2010;2, insulinoma&#x2010;associated antigen&#x2010;2; IAA, insulin autoantibody; ICA, islet cell antibody; M, male; PD&#x2010;1, programmed cell death&#x2010;1; PD&#x2010;L1, programmed cell death ligand&#x2010;1; ZnT8, zinc transporter&#xA0;8.</p>
